data.description: 55+ gated community of Ovation at Mtn Falls Golf Club. Extended garage for large vehicles, plantation shutters throughout, ceiling surround sound home theater in living room, and finished landscaping. Open kitchen boasts large island w/ pendant lights, walk-in pantry, upgraded cabinets w/ soft close hinges and whirlpool stainless steel appliances. Primary suite has dual sinks, walk-in shower, walk-in closet w/ door to patio. Backyard features covered patio with pavers, artificial grass, electric hook ups for entertainment. Premium lot w/ no rear neighbor offers privacy, epic views, walkway along side of home, and grand curb appeal. Soft water loop installed. Community offers heated pool, 2nd clubhouse, billiard lounge, tennis, pickleball, and gym. 18-hole golf course, main clubhouse, driving range, restaurant. Ovation community offers exclusive clubhouse/amenities separate from Mtn Falls, ovation residents have access to both.
